	<h1 class="title">那些形式主义的时装，就好像从火星来到了地球|巴黎时装周评论</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Vanessa Friedman</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-03 07:56:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15662/medium/15662.jpg?1443745488" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15662" data-title="《那些形式主义的时装，就好像从火星来到了地球|巴黎时装周评论》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15662/medium/15662.jpg?1443745488" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15662.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
		<!-- 新浪微博 -->
		<a data-ga-event="mobile:share:weibo" href="http://service.weibo.com/share/share.php" class="share iconfont icon-weibo" ></a>
